.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C337088DF76AB12BB182FCBC337940C3" pageId="31" pageNumber="552" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F76AB12BB182FCBC337940C3" blockId="31.[151,1437,223,897]" pageId="31" pageNumber="552">
COMMENTS: Wahlberg’s journal and labelled specimens show that he was in Durban from March to early 
<date id="FF937DC6F76AB12BB1D2FC98330240C3" box="[151,315,871,897]" pageId="31" pageNumber="552" value="1840-10">October 1840</date>
.
